  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We&apos;re Celebrating Reading Glasses Day on June 7!    Reading Glasses Day (RGD) is a commemorative date dedicated to raising awareness about the lack of access to reading glasses in developing countries, and the impact that glasses have on people&apos;s lives.   Our goal is to raise $20,000 to create access to glasses for 25,000 people living in impoverished communities in Angola, Democratic Republic of the Congo, and Tanzania. Thanks to our Board, every dollar donated up to $10,000 will be matched!</narrative>
  </description>
